snippet.title: My Imaginary Friend- Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description: My imaginary Friend is a first-person horror game that focuses on psychological horror. Set in the mandela catalogue universe, My Imaginary Friend is a 3d realistic first person horror game that features how AI uses the imagination of children to generate intruders and potentially alternates.
